data.description: Three bedroom brick, ranch home that has tons of updates including an eat-in kitchen with new cabinets, granite countertop, stainless steel appliances, and fixtures. The living room offers lots of natural light with windows that allow for flexible furniture placement, new flooring, and neutral paint that continue throughout the rest of the home including into the three bedrooms which also have new lighting fixtures. The home also has a fully remodeled bathroom with a full tub/shower, new toilet, vanity, sink, and fixtures. Additional updates to the home include a new roof, gas furnace, central air conditioner, hot water tank, gas service line, electrical service line/breaker box, exterior front/rear doors, garage door opener, and interior water lines. Located on a cul-de-sac street and near Elm Leaf Park and Route 51.
